            "value": "Update QuotaKit Mac to 0.27.0 (fork build 65.2 or later) for the new dedicated cards plus the v0.27 existing-provider extensions. iPhone 1.8.0 also remains forward-compatible with Mac 0.26.x and 65.1 — new tiles just stay hidden until Mac is on 65.2."
