    "The Daily Spend chart on the Cost tab now scrolls through your full accumulated history, and QuotaKit Pro now gates provider, cost, history, sharing, merge, and visible notification features for real synced data.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Daily Spend chart on the Cost tab now scrolls through your full accumulated history, and QuotaKit Pro now gates provider, cost, history, sharing, merge, and visible notification features for real synced data."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「コスト」タブの Daily Spend グラフが蓄積された全履歴をスクロールできるようになり、QuotaKit Pro は実同期データのプロバイダー、コスト、履歴、共有、統合、表示通知機能をゲートするようになりました。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“成本”标签页的 Daily Spend 图表现在可滚动查看完整累积历史，QuotaKit Pro 也会为真实同步数据限制提供商、成本、历史、分享、合并和可见通知功能。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「成本」分頁的 Daily Spend 圖表現在可捲動查看完整累積歷史，QuotaKit Pro 也會為真實同步資料限制提供商、成本、歷史、分享、合併和可見通知功能。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "QuotaKit Pro — Free mode keeps one selected synced provider plus basic quota details, while Pro and demo mode unlock the full provider list, cost dashboard, history charts, share actions, advanced merge controls, and visible quota alerts.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QuotaKit Pro — Free mode keeps one selected synced provider plus basic quota details, while Pro and demo mode unlock the full provider list, cost dashboard, history charts, share actions, advanced merge controls, and visible quota alerts."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QuotaKit Pro — Free モードでは、選択した同期済みプロバイダー 1 つと基本的なクォータ詳細を維持します。Pro とデモモードでは、全プロバイダー一覧、コストダッシュボード、履歴グラフ、共有アクション、詳細な統合コントロール、表示型クォータ通知が解除されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QuotaKit Pro — Free 模式保留一个已选择的同步提供商和基础额度详情；Pro 和演示模式解锁完整提供商列表、成本仪表盘、历史图表、分享操作、高级合并控制和可见额度提醒。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QuotaKit Pro — Free 模式保留一個已選擇的同步提供商和基本額度詳情；Pro 和示範模式解鎖完整提供商列表、成本儀表板、歷史圖表、分享操作、進階合併控制和可見額度提醒。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
